== Crane Fever ==

A UFO catcher (crane game) mini-game.

=== How to Play ===

# Control crane position with D-Pad
# Press A to drop the claw
# Try to grab Kirby dolls
# Each doll = 1 extra life

=== Tips ===

* Time the drop carefully
* Aim for center of Kirby dolls
* Some positions easier than others
* Practice improves success rate

== Egg Catcher ==

Catch eggs thrown by King Dedede.

=== How to Play ===

# Dedede throws objects from above
# Move Kirby left/right to catch
# Catch eggs for points
# Avoid bombs

=== Scoring ===

{| class="wikitable"
! Item !! Effect
|-
| Egg || Points, life at threshold
|-
| Bomb || Game over
|}

=== Tips ===

* Watch Dedede's throwing pattern
* Bombs look different from eggs
* Move quickly between catches
* High scores earn more lives

== Quick Draw ==

Reaction-time shooting contest.

=== How to Play ===

# Face off against opponent
# Wait for "FIRE!" signal
# Press A as fast as possible
# Faster draw wins

=== Opponents ===

Multiple opponents with varying difficulty:
* Early rounds: Slow opponents
* Later rounds: Faster opponents
* Final round: Very challenging

=== Tips ===

* Don't press early (disqualification)
* Watch for the exact signal
* Stay focused
* Practice improves reaction time

